~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : shout                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : shout <message>

   This allows you to "shout" to the whole talker. Shortcut is '!'.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : say, tell
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
